data.title: Georges Street
data.meta_description: FLYEfit Georges Street is a gym with fitness classes, astro studio, personal training available and a large selection of free weight equipment
data.text:
FLYEfit Georges Street is located right in the middle of Georges Street, just opposite the iconic Georges Street Arcade. Previously an old church building, this 20,000 sq ft gym has everything a fitness lover would need from a heavy lifting area and free weights section on the ground floor to a top floor mezzanine for Yoga and Pilates. This gym also has a large cardio and strength area, a large Astro area and a private spin studio.

Located less than five minutes from Grafton Street, this gym is easily accessible with bus routes stopping right outside.
